  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_141",
    "english": "Demon, a member of the onis. They can usually be seen in places with a strong demonic presence. Their demonic energy gathers in their core in the middle of their body, boiling, and they release this energy to attack with powerful magic. Because of the unstable energy, it's hard to control their attacks, making them use supplementary tools like wands that don't match their size.",
